reviewText:
If you are searching for the best porn anthology featuring, porn goddess, Jenna Jameson, at her best, look elsewhere; for the misleading product description led me to waste my hard earned money on this piece of crap, which constitutes nothing more than an anthology featuring some of Jenna Jameson's favorite porn stars posing either nude or semi-nude and is indistinguishable from Penthouse or Playboy Playmate of the Year videos. Stay away at all cost.

You'd be better served watching Playmate of the Year videos.
Old and out dated. Don't waste your money on this on. Bought it for a gag gift, but the gag was on me.

Dont buy this if your looking for Jenna at here best, its actually at her worst, you might as well throw 25 bucks in the street and walk away.  If you want to see more than Nikki nova moving her shoulders, then you'll be dissapointed.  I gave it two stars cause i found Selena in it(what happened to her?), and some models in the Bonus sections were cool, as well as I like some softcore, but this dvd didn't even break out backsides.  There's better on Amazon for less.
